						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the compound of the Vīrabhadrasvāmi temple.</p>						

						<p>ĀNANDA.</p>						

						<p>This record is dated in the cyclic year Ānanda, Śrāvana, ba. 2.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record the gifts of land to the temple of Vīrabhadrasvāmi for maintaining perpetual lamps.</p>						

						</summary>
